  <section>
    <h3 id="gyroscope">
      Gyroscope
    </h3>
    <p>
      The <dfn for="PermissionName" enum-value>"gyroscope"</dfn>
      permission is the permission associated with the usage of the
      [[gyroscope]] API.

      Its <a>permission revocation algorithm</a> is the result of calling
